      • runTestProcedure

        public java.util.List<TestRun> runTestProcedure(java.lang.String orderNo,
                                                java.lang.String description,
                                                java.lang.Integer type,
                                                java.lang.Integer procedureID,
                                                java.lang.String patientID,
                                                java.lang.String givenName,
                                                java.lang.String dateOfBirth,
                                                java.lang.String patientEthnicity,
                                                java.lang.String patientGender,
                                                java.lang.String patientHeight,
                                                java.lang.String patientWeight,
                                                java.util.List<java.lang.String> patientMeds,
                                                java.lang.String patientTemp,
                                                java.lang.String patientHeartRate,
                                                java.lang.String patientOLevel,
                                                java.lang.String diastolicBP,
                                                java.lang.String systolicBP,
                                                java.lang.String meal,
                                                java.lang.String hydration,
                                                java.lang.String oilContent,
                                                java.lang.String skinColor,
                                                java.lang.String specimen,
                                                java.lang.String luminosity,
                                                java.lang.String red,
                                                java.lang.String blue,
                                                java.lang.String green,
                                                java.lang.String imageFile,
                                                java.lang.Integer searchRowId,
                                                int index,
                                                javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request)
                                         throws java.lang.Exception
        Run Acquisition on Spectrometer and get the data for every Procedure Repeat
        Parameters:
        orderNo - Order Number of the Run
        description - Description given in Order Details Page
        type - Spectra Type
        procedureID - ID of the Procedure to use for Run
        patientID - ID of the Patient
        givenName - Given Name of the Patient
        dateOfBirth - Date of Birth of the Patient
        patientEthnicity - Ethnicity of the Patient
        patientGender - Gender of the Patient
        patientHeight - Height of the Patient
        patientWeight - Weight of the Patient
        patientMeds - Medications of the Patient
        patientTemp - Temperature of the Patient
        patientHeartRate - Heart Rate of the Patient
        patientOLevel - Oxygen Level of the Patient
        diastolicBP - Diastolic BP of the Patient
        systolicBP - Systolic BP of the Patient
        meal - Time since Last meal for the Patient
        hydration - Hydration on specimen of the Patient (For Skin)
        oilContent - Oil Content on specimen of the Patient (For Skin)
        skinColor - Skin Color at Skin specimen of the patient (For Skin)
        specimen - Specimen of the patient on which run is taken (For Skin)
        luminosity - Luminosity value at Skin specimen of the patient (For Skin)
        red - Red Scale value at Skin specimen of the patient (For Skin)
        blue - Blue Scale value at Skin specimen of the patient (For Skin)
        green - Green Scale value at Skin specimen of the patient (For Skin)
        imageFile - Image File of Skin value at Skin specimen of the patient (For Skin)
        searchRowId - Patient ID
        index - index which shows which Procedure Repeat is this
        request -
        Returns:
        List of TestRun objects for all different segments
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
